# Animated Characters Login Page

Split-screen login page with four animated cartoon characters (purple, black, orange, yellow) on the left panel. Characters track the cursor with their eyes, lean toward mouse movement, and react when typing a password — the purple character sneaks a peek when the password is visible.

## Use when
- Building a login or authentication page with a playful, engaging cartoon mascot experience.
- Demonstrating brand personality that is warm, fun, and interactive.
- Creating an interactive demo that showcases cursor-tracking animations.

## Stack
- Framework: react
- Libraries: lucide-react, @radix-ui/react-slot, class-variance-authority, @radix-ui/react-checkbox, @radix-ui/react-label
- Requires: tailwind, shadcn

## Install
```bash
lucide-react, @radix-ui/react-slot, class-variance-authority, @radix-ui/react-checkbox, @radix-ui/react-label
```

